ActInternational Development Research Centre Act
PrecisAppointment of FAITH MITCHELL of Washington, District of Columbia, to be a governor of the Board of Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Dan M. Martin, whose term has expired.
